\n              - button \"Image 6\" [ref=e1059] [cursor=pointer]\n        - generic [ref=e1061]:\n          - generic [ref=e1062]:\n            - generic [ref=e1063]:\n              - heading \"Description\" [level=2] [ref=e1064]\n              - img [ref=e1066]\n            - paragraph [ref=e1070]: Powerful and reliable, the AK-47 is one of the most popular assault rifles in the world. It is most deadly in short, controlled bursts of fire. A custom paint job has been applied which can only be described as \"black on black on slate black\". \"Call a doctor, they're gonna need one\"\n          - generic [ref=e1071]:\n            - generic [ref=e1072]:\n              - img [ref=e1073]\n              - heading \"History\" [level=3] [ref=e1075]\n            - paragraph [ref=e1076]: The AK-47 | Slate was first introduced to CS2 4 years ago, on May 3rd, 2021. It was released as part of the Snakebite Case, alongside the \"Snakebite Case\" update. The skin was created by the community designer \"Redesired\".\n          - generic [ref=e1077]:\n            - generic [ref=e1078]:\n              - img [ref=e1079]\n              - heading \"Origin\" [level=3] [ref=e1081]\n            - paragraph [ref=e1082]: The AK-47 | Slate can be obtained by opening a Snakebite Case container. The skin is also part of the The Snakebite Collection.\n          - generic [ref=e1083]:\n            - generic [ref=e1084]:\n              - img [ref=e1085]\n              - heading \"Popularity\" [level=3] [ref=e1087]\n            - paragraph [ref=e1088]: With a popularity of 99%, the AK-47 | Slate is currently extremely popular, which makes it one of the most popular items in CS2. This popularity measurement is based on the daily sales volume and the price of the skin.\n          - generic [ref=e1089]:\n            - generic [ref=e1090]:\n              - img [ref=e1091]\n              - heading \"Rarity\" [level=3] [ref=e1093]\n            - paragraph [ref=e1094]: The AK-47 | Slate is one of 318 other Rifle skins. The rarity of the skin is Restricted, which makes the Slate a rather rare drop with an estimated drop chance of 15.98%.\n          - generic [ref=e1095]:\n            - generic [ref=e1096]:\n              - img [ref=e1097]\n              - heading \"Availability\" [level=3] [ref=e1099]\n            - paragraph [ref=e1100]: With a price range between $4.05 and $49.99, the AK-47 | Slate is a very affordable skin. Fortunately, it's currently widely available and can be purchased on multiple different markets.\n          - generic [ref=e1101]:\n            - generic [ref=e1102]:\n              - img [ref=e1103]\n              - heading \"Versions\" [level=3] [ref=e1105]\n            - paragraph [ref=e1106]: The float value of the AK-47 | Slate ranges from 0.00 to 1.00, which makes the skin available in all exteriors. For each exterior, there also exists a StatTrak version for the Slate.\n          - generic [ref=e1107]:\n            - generic [ref=e1108]:\n              - img [ref=e1109]\n              - heading \"Finish Style\" [level=3] [ref=e1111]\n            - paragraph [ref=e1112]: This AK-47 has been painted in a \"Gunsmith\" style, with the Slate finish. This style uses a combination of patina and custom paint styles. That said, this particular skin has been mostly painted in shades of black. Different pattern indexes have no effect on the Slate finish. The skin uses the old legacy model.\n          - generic [ref=e1113]:\n            - generic [ref=e1114]:\n              - img [ref=e1115]\n              - heading \"Community Sentiment\" [level=3] [ref=e1117]\n            - paragraph [ref=e1118]: The AK-47 | Slate has received over 1.5K votes on CSGOSKINS.GG, leading to an average rating of 4.4 out of 5 stars. The skin is currently also owned by the professional CS2 players kennys, s1mple and taz.\n        - generic [ref=e1119]:\n          - generic [ref=e1120]:\n            - heading \"Similar AK-47 Skins\" [level=2] [ref=e1121]\n            - i