| Uncharted (Factory New)\" [ref=e476]\n                - generic [ref=e477]:\n                  - generic [ref=e478]: Starting at\n                  - generic [ref=e480]: $2.37\n                - link \"View\" [ref=e482] [cursor=pointer]:\n                  - /url: /item/ak-47-uncharted\n              - generic [ref=e483]:\n                - generic [ref=e484]: AK-47 | Black Laminate (Factory New)\n                - link \"  AK-47 | Black Laminate (Factory New)\" [ref=e485] [cursor=pointer]:\n                  - /url: /item/ak-47-black-laminate\n                  - generic [ref=e486]:\n                    - generic:  \n                    - img \"AK-47 | Black Laminate (Factory New)\" [ref=e487]\n                - generic [ref=e488]:\n                  - generic [ref=e489]: Starting at\n                  - generic [ref=e491]: $230.00\n                - link \"View\" [ref=e493] [cursor=pointer]:\n                  - /url: /item/ak-47-black-laminate\n              - generic [ref=e494]:\n                - generic [ref=e495]: AK-47 | Steel Delta (Factory New)\n                - link \"  AK-47 | Steel Delta (Factory New)\" [ref=e496] [cursor=pointer]:\n                  - /url: /item/ak-47-steel-delta\n                  - generic [ref=e497]:\n                    - generic:  \n                    - img \"AK-47 | Steel Delta (Factory New)\" [ref=e498]\n                - generic [ref=e499]:\n                  - generic [ref=e500]: Starting at\n                  - generic [ref=e502]: $22.79\n                - link \"View\" [ref=e504] [cursor=pointer]:\n                  - /url: /item/ak-47-steel-delta\n              - generic [ref=e505]:\n                - generic [ref=e506]: AK-47 | Midnight Laminate (Factory New)\n                - link \"  AK-47 | Midnight Laminate (Factory New)\" [ref=e507] [cursor=pointer]:\n                  - /url: /item/ak-47-midnight-laminate\n                  - generic [ref=e508]:\n                    - generic:  \n                    - img \"AK-47 | Midnight Laminate (Factory New)\" [ref=e509]\n                - generic [ref=e510]:\n                  - generic [ref=e511]: Starting at\n                  - generic [ref=e513]: $34.68\n                - link \"View\" [ref=e515] [cursor=pointer]:\n                  - /url: /item/ak-47-midnight-laminate\n              - generic [ref=e516]:\n                - generic [ref=e517]: AK-47 | Neon Rider (Factory New)\n                - link \"  AK-47 | Neon Rider (Factory New)\" [ref=e518] [cursor=pointer]:\n                  - /url: /item/ak-47-neon-rider\n                  - generic [ref=e519]:\n                    - generic:  \n                    - img \"AK-47 | Neon Rider (Factory New)\" [ref=e520]\n                - generic [ref=e521]:\n                  - generic [ref=e522]: Starting at\n                  - generic [ref=e524]: $352.17\n                - link \"View\" [ref=e526] [cursor=pointer]:\n                  - /url: /item/ak-47-neon-rider\n              - generic [ref=e527]:\n                - generic [ref=e528]: AK-47 | Jet Set (Factory New)\n                - link \"  AK-47 | Jet Set (Factory New)\" [ref=e529] [cursor=pointer]:\n                  - /url: /item/ak-47-jet-set\n                  - generic [ref=e530]:\n                    - generic:  \n                    - img \"AK-47 | Jet Set (Factory New)\" [ref=e531]\n                - generic [ref=e532]:\n                  - generic [ref=e533]: Starting at\n                  - generic [ref=e535]: $1 051.67\n                - link \"View\" [ref=e537] [cursor=pointer]:\n                  - /url: /item/ak-47-jet-set\n          - link \"Show all\" [ref=e538] [cursor=pointer]:\n            - /url: /weapons/ak-47\n          - generic [ref=e539]:\n            - heading \"Description\" [level=2] [ref=e540]\n            - generic [ref=e541]:\n              - generic [ref=e542]:\n                - generic [ref=e543]:\n                  - img [ref=e544]\n                  - heading \"Overview\" [level=3] [ref=e546]\n                - paragraph [ref=e548]: The AK-47 | Slate is robed in hues of grey and black, resembling the sleek texture of slate stone. This assault rifle skin is part of Shattered Web Collection and was unveiled in November 2019.\n              - generic [ref=e549]:\n                - generic [ref=e550]:\n                  - img [ref=e551]\n                  - heading \"Rarity\" [level=3] [ref=e553]\n                - paragraph [ref=e555]: Labeled as 'Restricted', the AK-47 | Slate is a rare gem with a limited drop rate. Its sleek, modern design makes it one of the most favored CS:GO skins.\n              - generic [ref=e556]:\n                - generic [ref=e557]:\n                  - img [ref=e558]\n                  - heading \"History\" [level=3] [ref=e560]\n                - paragraph [ref=e562]: This skin was launched on the CS:GO market as a part of Shattered Web Collection in November 2019.\n              - generic [ref=e563]:\n                - generic [ref=e564]:\n                  - img [ref=e565]\n                  - heading \"Popularity\" [level=3] [ref=e567]\n                - paragraph [ref=e569]: The AK-47 | Slate has gained significant popularity among the gaming community due to its sophisticated design and tactful theme.\n              - generic [ref=e570]:\n                - generic [ref=e571]:\n                  - img [ref=e572]\n                  - heading \"Compatibility\" [level=3] [ref=e574]\n                - paragraph [ref=e576]: This skin is compatible solely with the AK-47 - the go-to assault rifle for CS:GO veterans.\n              - generic [ref=e577]:\n                - generic [ref=e578]:\n                  - img [ref=e579]\n                  - heading \"Unique Features\" [level=3] [ref=e581]\n                - paragraph [ref=e583]: The unique feature of the Slate skin lies in its monochromatic design, portraying an aura of elegance and power.\n              - generic [ref=e584]:\n                - generic [ref=e585]:\n                  - img [ref=e586]\n                  - heading \"Event\" [level=3] [ref=e588]\n                - paragraph [ref=e590]: Introduced through the Shattered Web Collection, it offered an assortment of new skins, tasks, and rewards for players.\n              - generic [ref=e591]:\n                - generic [ref=e592]:\n                  - img [ref=e593]\n                  - heading \"Trivia\" [level=3] [ref=e595]\n                - paragraph [ref=e597]: The inspiration behind the skin design is drawn from the aesthetic appeal of natural slate rock. Its sleek and polished finish aids to its popularity among the masses.\n              - generic [ref=e598]:\n                - generic [ref=e599]:\n                  - img [ref=e600]\n                  - heading \"Skin Designer\" [level=3] [ref=e602]\n                - paragraph [ref=e604]: Designed by Redesired.\n              - generic [ref=e605]:\n                - generic [ref=e606]:\n                  - img [ref=e607]\n                  - heading \"Technical Features\" [level=3] [ref=e609]\n                - paragraph [ref=e611]: The skin design showcases impressive texturing and color grading, effectively mimicking the appearance of slate rock texture.\n              - generic [ref=e612]:\n                - generic [ref=e613]:\n                  - img [ref=e614]\n                  - heading \"Reviews and Ratings\" [level=3] [ref=e616]\n                - paragraph [ref=e618]: Boasting high praise for its stylish and minimalistic design, the AK-47 | Slate ranks among the favorite picks in the CS:GO community.\n              - generic [ref=e619]:\n                - generic [ref=e620]:\n                  - img [ref=e621]\n                  - heading \"Historical Significance\" [level=3] [ref=e623]\n                - paragraph [ref=e625]: The release of the AK-47 | Slate marked a turn towards more refined and sophisticated designs in the realm of CS:GO skins.\n              - generic [ref=e626]:\n                - generic [ref=e627]:\n                  - img [ref=e628]\n                  - heading \"Reasons for Popularity\" [level=3] [ref=e630]\n                - paragraph [ref=e632]: The AK-47 | Slate owes its popularity to the iconic weapon it transforms and the unique, sleek design it flaunts.\n              - generic [ref=e633]:\n                - generic [ref=e634]:\n                  - img [ref=e635]\n                  - heading \"Influential Events\" [level=3] [ref=e637]\n                - paragraph [ref=e639]: The unveiling of the AK-47 | Slate as part of the Shattered Web Collection played a crucial role in amassing its fame.\n              - generic [ref=e640]:\n                - generic [ref=e641]:\n                  - img [ref=e642]\n                  - heading \"Creation Story\" [level=3] [ref=e644]\n                - paragraph [ref=e646]: The making AK-47 | Slate aimed to incorporate a taste of nature into the gaming universe, resulting in this elegant and unique skin.\n              - generic [ref=e647]:\n                - generic [ref=e648]:\n                  - img [ref=e649]\n                  - heading \"Symbolism and Design Elements\" [level=3] [ref=e651]\n                - paragraph [ref=e653]: The design elements of this skin symbolize power and sophistication - elements that quintessentially define the ethos of every CS:GO battle.\n              - generic [ref=e654]:\n                - generic [ref=e655]:\n                  - img [ref=e656]\n                  - heading \"Emotional Connection\" [level=3] [ref=e658]\n                - paragraph [ref=e660]: The exclusive design and weapon preference make this skin a treasured possession for many CS:GO enthusiasts.\n              - generic [ref=e661]:\n                - generic [ref=e662]:\n                  - img [ref=e663]\n                  - heading \"Impact on Community\" [level=3] [ref=e665]\n                - paragraph [ref=e667]: The AK-47 | Slate skin sets a precedent in the gaming community for its realistic texture and natural design, encouraging more distinctive and innovative skin designs.\n              - generic [ref=e668]:\n                - generic [ref=e669]:\n                  - img [ref=e670]\n                  - heading \"Usage in Esports\" [level=3] [ref=e672]\n                - paragraph [ref=e674]: Being a favorite skin for one of the most coveted weapons, the AK-47 | Slate makes an occasional appearance on big CS:GO Esports stages.\n              - generic [ref=e675]:\n                - generic [ref=e676]:\n                  - img [ref=e677]\n                  - heading \"Player Stories\" [level=3] [ref=e679]\n                - paragraph [ref=e681]: There are numerous stories of players obtaining the AK-47 | Slate skin, even in esports environments, where it is viewed as a mark of in-game prestige.\n  - contentinfo [ref=e682]:\n    - generic [ref=e683]:\n      - generic [ref=e684]:\n        - link \"Home link in footer\" [ref=e685] [cursor=pointer]:\n          - /url: /\n          - img [ref=e686]\n        - generic [ref=e693]:\n          - generic [ref=e694]:\n            - link \"Twitter\" [ref=e695] [cursor=pointer]:\n              - /url: https://x.com/CSMarketCapCom\n              - img [ref=e696]\n            - link \"Telegram\" [ref=e698] [cursor=pointer]:\n              - /url: https://t.me/csmarketcap\n              - img [ref=e699]\n            - link \"VK page\" [ref=e701] [cursor=pointer]:\n              - /url: https://vk.com/csmarketcap\n              - img [ref=e702]\n            - link \"Discord\" [ref=e704] [cursor=pointer]:\n              - /url: /discord\n              - generic [ref=e705]: \n            - link \"trustpilot\" [ref=e706] [cursor=pointer]:\n              - /url: https://www.trustpilot.com/review/csmarketcap.com\n              - img [ref=e707]\n          - generic [ref=e709]: 2026 © CSMARKETCAP.COM\n      - generic [ref=e711]:\n        - generic [ref=e712]:\n          - generic [ref=e713]: 